ople use them to keep themselves warm.\n|-\n!scope=\"row\" rowspan=2| {{anchor|Darmanitan}} Darmanitan\n!scope=\"row\" rowspan=2| {{nihongo||\u30d2\u30d2\u30c0\u30eb\u30de|Hihidaruma}}\n| rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\"| {{nts|555}}\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#f08030; text-align:center;\"| Fire\n| rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center; background:#ececec; vertical-align:middle; font-size:smaller; text-align:center;\" class=\"table-na\"| Does not evolve\n|Can change between \"Zen mode\" and Normal mode\n|-\n| style=\"background:#f08030; text-align:center;\"| Fire\n| style=\"background:#ff6996; text-align:center;\"| Psychic\n| \"Zen Mode\"\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| {{anchor|Maractus}} Maractus\n!scope=\"row\"| {{nihongo||\u30de\u30e9\u30ab\u30c3\u30c1|Marakatchi}}\n|align=center| {{nts|556}}\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#2dcd45; text-align:center;\"| Grass\n| {{n/a|Does not evolve}}\n|\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| {{anchor|Dwebble}} Dwebble\n!scope=\"row\"| {{nihongo||\u30a4\u30b7\u30ba\u30de\u30a4|Ishizumai}}\n|align=center| {{nts|557}}\n| style=\"background:#a8b820; text-align:center;\"| Bug\n| style=\"background:#b8a038; text-align:center;\"| Rock\n|align=center| [[#Curstle|Crustle (#558)]]\n|\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| {{anchor|Crustle}} Crustle\n!scope=\"row\"| {{nihongo||\u30a4\u30ef\u30d1\u30ec\u30b9|Iwaparesu}}\n|align=center| {{nts|558}}\n| style=\"background:#a8b820; text-align:center;\"| Bug\n| style=\"background:#b8a038; text-align:center;\"| Rock\n| {{n/a|Does not evolve}}\n|\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| {{anchor|Scraggy}} Scraggy\n!scope=\"row\"| {{nihongo||\u30ba\u30eb\u30c3\u30b0|Zuruggu}}\n|align=center| {{nts|559}}\n| style=\"background:#5c483b; text-align:center;\"| {{font color|white|Dark}}\n| style=\"background:#94352d; text-align:center;\"| {{font color|white|Fighting}}\n|align=center| [[#Scrafty|Scrafty (#560)]]\n|\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| {{anchor|Scrafty}} Scrafty\n!scope=\"row\"| {{nihongo||\u30ba\u30eb\u30ba\u30ad\u30f3|Zuruzukin}}\n|align=cen