inning its body 360 degrees, it can dig easily through the ground.\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| {{anchor|Excadrill}} Excadrill\n!scope=\"row\"| {{nihongo||\u30c9\u30ea\u30e5\u30a6\u30ba|Dory\u016bzu}}\n|align=center| {{nts|530}}\n| style=\"background:#e0c068; text-align:center;\"| Ground\n| style=\"background:#b8b8d0; text-align:center;\"| Steel\n| {{n/a|Does not evolve}}\n|\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| {{anchor|Audino}} Audino\n!scope=\"row\"| {{nihongo||\u30bf\u30d6\u30f3\u30cd|Tabunne}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| {{nts|531}}\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#a8a878; text-align:center;\"| Normal\n|align=center| [[List of generation VI Pok\u00e9mon#Mega Audino|Mega Evolution]]\n|It can hear very well. Audino is the only Generation V Pok\u00e9mon with a Mega Evolution.\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| {{anchor|Timburr}} Timburr\n!scope=\"row\"| {{nihongo||\u30c9\u30c3\u30b3\u30e9\u30fc|Dokkor\u0101}}\n|align=center| {{nts|532}}\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#94352d; text-align:center;\"| {{font color|white|Fighting}}\n|align=center| [[#Gurdurr|Gurdurr (#533)]]\n|\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| {{anchor|Gurdurr}} Gurdurr\n!scope=\"row\"| {{nihongo||\u30c9\u30c6\u30c3\u30b3\u30c4|Dotekkotsu}}\n|align=center| {{nts|533}}\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#94352d; text-align:center;\"| {{font color|white|Fighting}}\n|align=center| [[#Conkeldurr|Conkeldurr (#534)]]\n|\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| {{anchor|Conkeldurr}} Conkeldurr\n!scope=\"row\"| {{nihongo||\u30ed\u30fc\u30d6\u30b7\u30f3|R\u014dbushin}}\n|align=center| {{nts|534}}\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#94352d; text-align:center;\"| {{font color|white|Fighting}}\n| {{n/a|Does not evolve}}\n|\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| {{anchor|Tympole}} Tympole\n!scope=\"row\"| {{nihongo||\u30aa\u30bf\u30de\u30ed|Otamaro}}\n|align=center| {{nts|535}}\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#149eff; text-align:center;\"| Water\n|align=center| [[#Palpitoad|Palpitoad (#536)]]\n|They communicate by vibrating their cheeks.\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| {{anchor|Palpitoad}} Pal