row\"|\"Ricky\"<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hotnewhiphop.com/ot-genasis-ricky-new-song.1964115.html|title=O.T. Genasis - Ricky|website=Hotnewhiphop.com}}</ref>\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n| rowspan=\"1\"|''Rhythm & Bricks''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"|\"O.V. (It's Over)\"<br><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(featuring [[Trae tha Truth]] and [[K Camp]])</span>\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n| ''{{n/a|Non-album single}}''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"|\"Do It\"<br><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(featuring [[Lil Wayne]])</span>\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|\n| rowspan=\"2\"|''Rhythm & Bricks''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"|\"[[Cut It (song)|Cut It]]\"<br><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(featuring [[Young Dolph]])</span>\n| 35 || 11 || 6 || 84 || \u2014\n|\n*RIAA: 2\u00d7 Platinum{{Certification Cite Ref|region=United States|type=single|title=Cut It|artist=O.T. Genasis}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"|\"Push It\"\n| 2016\n| \u2014{{efn|group=upper-alpha|\"Push It\" did not enter the ''Billboard'' Hot 100, but peaked at number 14 on the [[Bubbling Under Hot 100 Singles]] chart.<ref name=\"Bubbling\">{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/biz/search/charts?f%5B0%5D=ts_chart_artistname%3AO.T.%20Genasis&f%5B1%5D=itm_field_chart_id%3A344&f%5B2%5D=ss_bb_type%3Achart_item&type=2&artist=O.T.%20Genasis|title=Chart Search for O.T. Genasis (Bubbling Under Hot 100 Singles) {{!}} Billboard|work=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|accessdate=January 19, 2017}}</ref>}} || \u2014{{efn|group=upper-alpha|\"Push It\" did not enter the ''Billboard'' Hot R&B/Hip-Hop Songs chart, but peaked at number one on the Bubbling Under R&B/Hip-Hop Singles chart.<ref name=\"BubblingR&B\">{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/biz/search/charts?f[0]=ts_chart_artistname%3AO.T.%20Genasis&f[1]=itm_field_chart_id%3A345&f[2]=ss_bb_type%3Achart_item&type=2&artist=O.T.%20Genasis|title=Chart Search for O.T. Genasis (Bubbling Under R&B/Hip-Hop Singles) {{!}} Billboard|work=[[